      "role": "user",
      "content": "i cant even look at the news anymore. like everything is just... collapsing. every time i see a report on the heatwaves or the extinctions i just feel this pit in my stomach. what is even the point of building a life or planning anything for the future when the planet is literally dying? it feels so stupid to even try.",
